From: Battery Optimization Suite <battery@local>
Date: Mon, 20 Jul 2026 12:00:00 +0800
Subject: [PATCH] battery: schedutil rate-limit tuning
Adjusts schedutil governor rate-limit to reduce DVFS jitter.

仅修改 kernel/sched/cpufreq_schedutil.c,定义 SCHEDUTIL_UP_RATE_LIMIT_NS
为 2ms,降低轻载时频繁升降频造成的功耗。

注:本补丁不再修改 kernel/sched/fair.c 中的 EAS_BIAS_THRESHOLD_UTIL,
避免与天玑9400+ 厂商 EM 表强耦合导致大小核唤醒异常。

#ifndef 保护,6.6 内核通用。
---
 kernel/sched/cpufreq_schedutil.c | 5 +++++
 1 file changed, 5 insertions(+)
diff --git a/kernel/sched/cpufreq_schedutil.c b/kernel/sched/cpufreq_schedutil.c
--- a/kernel/sched/cpufreq_schedutil.c
+++ b/kernel/sched/cpufreq_schedutil.c
@@ -20,6 +20,11 @@
 #include <linux/sched/cpufreq.h>
 #include <trace/events/power.h>

+/* Battery optimization: Reduce frequency ramping speed for efficiency */
+#ifndef SCHEDUTIL_UP_RATE_LIMIT_NS
+#define SCHEDUTIL_UP_RATE_LIMIT_NS (2000 * NSEC_PER_USEC)
+#endif
+
 struct su_policy {
 	struct cpufreq_policy	*policy;

--
